title: #92Noon! Cronin/Talkers/Gleeman
description: Courtney Cronin is in studio for the entire first hour on Vikings football, Wild & NFL talkers during the middle hour, and Gleeman in studio for the final hour, with a surprise cold call from John Bonnes to wrap the show!
